Keller Williams Sun Valley Southern Idaho

data.description: Plenty of room for the entire family in this single level, 4 bed, 2.5 bath home sitting on over a quarter of an acre lot in the Morning Sun Subdivision. Boasting over 3100 sq. ft. this comfortable & spacious home offers all the amenities you might want. Open concept, split bedroom floor plan. Office space off of entryway with 2 closets. Tile flooring in the entryway, kitchen and formal dining area. Granite countertops, & walk-in pantry in kitchen. Gas fireplace & 9ft ceiling in living room. Master suite with coffered ceiling. Barn door between master suite & the master bathroom with his & her walk-in closets. Tile flooring & surround in shower w/separate jetted tub. All bedrooms have walk-in closets. Tile flooring & surround in hall bathroom w/granite countertop. Laundry room w/granite countertops. 2nd washer/dryer in the finished 3 car garage. Nice vinyl fenced back yard with hot tub sitting on the partially covered patio. All newer wood shutters throughout & home security system in place. A must-see home!
